query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_properties,
  SUM(CASE WHEN sourceUrl IS NULL OR sourceUrl = '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as no_url,
  SUM(CASE WHEN sourceUrl IS NOT NULL AND sourceUrl != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_url
FROM properties
